<div class="text no-margin-bottom-on-texts aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12">
<div id="text-03fcd27268" class="cmp-text">
    <p>Moody’s delivers credit ratings, research, and a wide suite of data, analytics, and workflow solutions that help organizations understand risk and act with confidence. Agentic AI capabilities are embedded into our data ecosystem, deploying intelligent agents designed to uncover insights faster for smarter, more informed decisions.</p>

